imdb.title: Tatoeba Last Dungeon Mae no Mura no Shounen ga Joban no Machi de Kurasu Youna Monogatari
imdb.plot: Considered a weakling his entire life, novice adventurer Lloyd leaves his village located at the fringe of the mortal world to fulfill his dream of becoming a soldier.

episodes.title: Suppose a Kid from the Last Dungeon Boonies moved to a starter town
episodes.plot: Lloyd Belladonna comes to a town with the intention of being a soldier. He asks to stay at a witches house and says that he is very weak. But the witch soon discover that he may be the most powerful person in the town.

episodes.title: Suppose the Feeling of Being out of Place like the King of Beasts Lying Down in the Corner of the Petting Zoo
episodes.plot: Lloyd fails the exam. He decides to stay in the town and try again next year but for that he needs a job. He sees a flyer and goes to a restaurant for employment. But the owner is shocked and attacks him instinctively.

episodes.title: Suppose someone told you they'd do anything for you, which you appreciate but you know you should push back?
episodes.plot: The witches real identity is revealed. The true culprit behind the attacks on the town is revealed. The witch is in pinch.

episodes.title: Suppose the protagonist of a novel lead the story to a grand finale?
episodes.plot: The witch flees from the demon lord to find Lloyd. Lloyd searches for the witch and fights monsters thinking that those are just bugs.

episodes.title: Suppose someone took flirtation advise on a magazine way too seriously?
episodes.plot: An ancient and precious treasure is discovered and an important event is upcoming.

episodes.title: Suppose the obviously superior contestant wins, but the clearly inferior constestant also wins?
episodes.plot: It's the day of the inter-school match, the first team that wins two encounters will win the tournament. Who will get the Holy Sword?

episodes.title: Suppose it's looking like you need to clean up the mess, and you kind of saw it coming?
episodes.plot: The first break at the academy spent at a mysterious hotel.

episodes.title: Suppose you were just pretending to be lovers, but somehow the pretense transforms into the real deal!
episodes.plot: Other people comes at the hotel and finally the mystery between what is happening at the hotel is unveiled.

episodes.title: Suppose you visited an early dungeon but encountered three final bosses?
episodes.plot: Lloyds, Riho, Phyllo and Selen receives a mission coming directly from the King. Are they will able to complete it? There is also a mysterious guy after what there is in the dungeon Lloyd and the other are heading to.

episodes.title: Suppose a Kid from the Last Dungeon Boonies Moved to a Starter Town?
episodes.plot: The tour at Kunlun, Lloyd village. How would it be?

episodes.title: Suppose the villain starts appearing on and off like the middle part of a movie?
episodes.plot: An envy plan starts to run and it has something to do with the Last Dungeon.

episodes.title: Suppose a kid from the last dungeon boonies got used to life in a starter town?
episodes.plot: After coming back to Kunlun, Alka unveils her plan to get Lloyd quickly to the capital. In the meantime the exhibition match starts, and so Eug plan.
